{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "name": "3gods",
  "description": "One video covering three gods Hatmaster played — no opponents shown. Three vertical panels left-to-right ({my_god}, {my_god2}, {my_god3}), each card cropped to the top half of the splash art so every god is zoomed in on the face, feathered at the two seams. Each panel gets a cyan-glow icon badge and the god's name in a darkened bottom band. No VS marker — these are gods you played, not matchups. No auto headline (auto_headline: false) — the panel names already carry the god names; pass --text for an explicit headline. CLI: --god + --god2 + --god3 (skins via --skin/--skin2/--skin3, flips via --flip-god/--flip-god2/--flip-god3).",
  "auto_headline": false,
  "size": [
    1280,
    720
  ],
